data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! Beautiful large maintenance free home with loads of features in desirable location just four miles from Hayesville, NC. Lovely setting with lots of great landscaping already established including a small private pond in the backyard. This ranch style home features a 2 car attached garage, huge screened in back porch, inviting front porch and thats just part of the outdoor features. Inside, walk into a huge foyer with a great room to die for. Beautiful custom cabinetry, granite counters, huge 8' island and tons of prep space, etc. So much natural light from ample large windows and skylight in eat- kitchen area, living area features stacked stone f/p w/gas logs, Split floor plan with fantastic master suite, large closets, lovely bathrooms. Also, nice laundry room and huge bonus room perfect for office/study. Beautiful hardwood flooring thru out with tile in baths. Great room features vaulted ceiling, so spacious and roomy. Massive screened in back porch offers lots of privacy and overlooks the pond area. also includes all the furnishings except for some personal items. Located just 4 miles from Hayesville, right next to the Mountain Harbor Golf Course and Chatuge Lake is less than 5 minutes away. Less than 20 miles from Murphy. Too many nice features to for this custom built one owner home to name here. COME AND SEE!!!
